Title: Relates to credit unions
Summary: Establishes a credit union deposit program for the state to deposit a portion of funds under its control into credit unions.
LawCode: Add Art 2-D §§89 - 91, §454-a, Bank L; amd §§98-a & 105, St Fin L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the banking law and the state finance law, in relation to credit unions
